'''Colen of Greenpools''' is a minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Darren Killeen]] and only appears in &quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]]&quot;. Ser Colen is a [[Knighthood|knight]] serving King [[Renly Baratheon]] in the [[War of the Five Kings]].
